Source: pg-projection
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/suissa/pg_projection

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-projection
Architecture: all
Provides: postgresql-pg-projection
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: MongoDB-like JSONB projection helpers for PostgreSQL
  pg_projection adds MongoDB-style projection helpers for JSONB documents,
  including single-document and query-result projection functions.
